query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(pi it2) NoHashJoin(it2 pi n) NoMergeJoin(it2 n pi ci) NoMergeJoin(ci it2 n pi t mi) NoMergeJoin(ci it2 mi n pi t it1) */ select n.name
from person_info AS pi
inner join info_type AS it2
on pi.info_type_id = it2.id AND pi.info ilike '%usa%' AND it2.info ilike '%birth%'
inner join name AS n
on pi.person_id = n.id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on ci.person_id = n.id
inner join title AS t
on t.id = ci.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND ( mi.info ilike '%romance%' OR mi.info ilike '%action%')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.id = 3 group by n.name order by count(*) desc;
